# Project Overview

Chronicles Productivity is a task management application with React TypeScript frontend and Express with SQLite backend.

## Key Entry Points
- Frontend: [frontend/src/App.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/App.tsx) - Main application component
- Backend: [backend/src/index.ts](mdc:backend/src/index.ts) - Server entry point

## Main Directories
- [frontend/src/components](mdc:frontend/src/components) - React UI components
- [frontend/src/pages](mdc:frontend/src/pages) - Application pages/views
- [backend/src/controllers](mdc:backend/src/controllers) - Request handlers
- [backend/src/models](mdc:backend/src/models) - Database models
- [backend/src/routes](mdc:backend/src/routes) - API route definitions

